        <abstract>
            <p>Admires Edward Forbes’s theory of continental extensions, but it will discourage investigation of distribution.</p>
            <p>Mentions Oswald Heer’s proposed map of Atlantis.</p>
            <p>Discusses extinction of plants caused by the glacial era. Migration of plants and animals during glacial period.</p> 
<p>Encourages CL’s work [on <hi rend="italic">Antiquity of man</hi> (1863)].</p>  
<p>Comments on unfriendly reviews. Asks CL’s opinion about including a reply to reviewers in next edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
